<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/dffb0cc210e6ca60f7b0ec47d24543562.png"></span><span>Defense +20%</span></dt><dd><div>Increases defense by 20%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/e23fa30b574bf7f565547e4d26946c1f2.png"></span><span>Stun Res +100%</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to stun by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/dffb0cc210e6ca60f7b0ec47d24543562.png"></span><span>Deepest Dedication II</span></dt><dd><div>Grants the entire team a team defense amp<br>with a maximum team amp level of two when<br>the user's HP is restored.<br>After activating, this ability will not activate<br>again for 20 seconds.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurers at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div>・Some skills have different effects when used as a shared skill.</div><div>・Adventurers with the same name cannot be put into the same team.</div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. For a list of prizes and their appearance rates, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, and see Prizes under Appearance Rates.</div><div>3. If you obtain duplicate items from a tenfold summon or from using 10 single summon vouchers at once, the item quantities for each item will be combined when sent to the No Limit tab of your goodie box.</div><div>4. An Alberian Battle Royale skin for the adventurer featured in this summon showcase will be on sale and will cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1646287200,update_time1646186819